        <div id="about-us" style="background-color: white;">
            <h2 style="font-weight: bold;">About us</h2>
            <div style="margin: 2em;width:90vw;height:50vh;
        
            background-color: rgb(158, 189, 221);
            padding:1em;
            margin-left:4em;
        
            position:absolute;">
            <h3 style="font-weight: bold;">Vision</h3>
            <p>To provide support to the preliminary StartUp organisations to grow within themselves and thus
                be enabled to sustain themselves and benefit communities.</p>
            <h3 style="font-weight: bold;">Mission</h3>
            <p>To create a crowdfunding platform for the StartUp Businesses to enable them to
                build awareness in public and generate funding through free willing donations.</p>
            <h3 style="font-weight: bold;">Objective</h3>
            <ul style="text-align: justify;">
                <li>Provide a well designed, absolutely free of cost fundraising platform for the various StartUps in
                    need of
                    financial support and validation.</li>
                <li>Monitor and Evaluate the progress of the funds and support the organisations to make their ap- peal
                    more effective.</li>
                <li>Promote, advertise and enhance the publicity of the projects in order to make the market aware
                    of the various new ventures as well as appeals that can easily be fulfilled by the people through
                    individual donations.</li>

            </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="how-we-work" style="background-color:rgb(203, 212, 203);">
            <h2 style="font-weight: bold;">How we work</h2>
            <div style="width:90vw;height:50vh;
        
            background-color: lightslategrey;
            padding:1em;
            margin-left:4em;
           text-align: justify;
            position:absolute;">
                <p>
                    Starter friendly is a crowdfunding platform through which you can contribute small amounts to
                    startup business ventures.
                    Crowdfunding is
                    simple. You look at a project, an appeal and choose who you want to support in their business by
                    donating or sharing it on your social media.
                </p>

                <h2 style="font-weight: bold;">Steps:</h2>
                <ol>
                    <li>View the list of projects from the supported projects category on the home page. </li>
                    <li>Press learn more for the most appealing project according to you.</li>
                    <li>You can then read more about the startup and also see the details of the fundraiser so far .
                    <li>Click on the DONATE NOW button </li> on the project details page and choose from the fundraisers
                    that you would like to donate
                    to.</li>
                    <li>Press the DONATE NOW.You can donate online through Khalti for the transaction. </li>


                </ol>
            </div>


